        <num>CCRP 805</num>
        <heading>805.  Same; charge as to verdict acquitting on account of insanity</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 805.  Same; charge as to verdict acquitting on account of insanity
The court shall charge the jury that if it acquits a defendant on account of a plea of insanity it shall state that the defendant was found not guilty by reason of insanity.</p>
        </content>
